    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately not-assessed per ASME V&V 40 Table 1 MRL 2 scope. The CFD hemolysis model for the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump is deemed credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions in support of a Class II CPB device regulatory submission. The Claim (https://uofa.net/synth/claim/morrison-cpb-worst-case-hemolysis) and Requirement (https://uofa.net/synth/req/morrison-cpb-hemolysis-mrl2) documents fully specify the intended use scope including device class, patient population, and operating envelope.",
